sentences.sContent: If I squint with all my strength I may see it.
sentences.sContent_eng: If I squint with all my strength I may see it.
sentences.sCn: 如果我斜视与我所有的力量我可以看到它。

sentences.sContent: Aiming at the interferometric phase wrapping in squint model, a novel interferometric inverse synthetic aperture radar(ISAR) imaging algorithm based on dominant scatterers is proposed.
sentences.sContent_eng: Aiming at the interferometric phase wrapping in squint model, a novel interferometric inverse synthetic aperture radar(ISAR) imaging algorithm based on dominant scatterers is proposed.
sentences.sCn: 针对雷达在斜视工作下的干涉相位模糊问题，提出了一种新的特显点干涉逆合成孔径雷达（ISAR）成像算法。

trans.tranOther: to have each eye looking in a slightly different direction
